title: Live Luxe By Jennifer Lopez For Women. Eau De Parfum Spray 3.4 OZ
description: Launched by the design house of Jennifer Lopez.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: Benefit Cosmetics Full-Finish Lipstick Espionage
description: What it is:A full-finish lipstick.What it does:Your search for the perfect lipstick is over: Benefit Love Your Look Lipstick is a range of sumptuous shades for the lip that longs for full, rich color. Benefit's Love Your Look Makeup to Match Your Lifestyle collection takes the guesswork out of gorgeous. Choose from three unique looks: The Lana (light neutral shades), The Gabbi (medium neutral shades), and The Betty (deep neutral shades).What else you need to know:Now that your lips are flaunt-able, find a complementary Love Your Look creaseless cream shadow/liner and sheer cream blusher to complete your look. Go for a "lifestyle look" or, be daring and mix and match. All of the beautiful shades for lips, eyes, and cheeks will let you create the look you want. Plus, you'll love the hidden surprise: a "beauty fortune" inside every package.

title: VOGUE PROFESSIONAL ® My MANICURIST ® Budget Priced Fast Electric Powerful Manicure Pedicure Professional Salon Nail Drill File for Gels, Acrylics, Natural Nails. Turbo Nail Filing system. Control box for easy speed adjustment. Bits fit Vogue Dremel Kupa. INCLUDES 5 Diamond Bits, 5 sanding bands, 1 pc Mandrel . Model 2014
description:
VOGUE Professional  / My Manicurist  is a Budget priced drill for doing professional nails at home or for professional use.
Ideal for beauty student, nail salon.
Electrical/Plug-in Drill in 110V (for USA, Canada, Mexico).
Powerful: 3000-18,000 RPM Variable Speed.
FEATHERLIGHT Handpiece is easy slide-in/out type chuck. No need for an additional tool (wrench) to insert or remove an attachment.
Forward/Reverse selection.
Comes complete with hard-to-find, and usually expensive attachments, such as couple of diamond bits.
Sanding Bands included.
Standard chuck of 3/32" shank size (professional attachments will fit). Any additional attachments (not included) will fit the handpiece as long as the shank size is 3/32".
Comes with Separate Control Box for precision speed control. Sale is final due to FDA regulations
